# Superpowers Skills Reference

Skills are in `.cursor/skills/`. The `sessionStart` hook automatically injects `using-superpowers` skill.

## Quick Reference

| Skill | When to Use |
|-------|-------------|
| `brainstorming` | Before any creative work |
| `writing-plans` | Before implementation, after design |
| `executing-plans` | Execute plans in batches |
| `subagent-driven-development` | Execute plans with subagents |
| `test-driven-development` | Before writing ANY code |
| `systematic-debugging` | When encountering bugs |
| `verification-before-completion` | Before claiming done |
| `using-git-worktrees` | When starting feature work |
| `finishing-a-development-branch` | When implementation complete |
| `requesting-code-review` | After tasks/features |
| `receiving-code-review` | When receiving feedback |
| `dispatching-parallel-agents` | For 2+ independent tasks |

